1. Executive Summary

Overview

Modern production support environments require engineers to manually investigate application failures by collecting logs from multiple sources, analyzing error messages, identifying root causes, and preparing client communications. This process is time-consuming, repetitive, and dependent on individual expertise.

The VisualCron AI Production Support Agent introduces Artificial Intelligence into the incident investigation workflow by automating log collection, failure analysis, and Root Cause Analysis (RCA) generation while maintaining complete human control over customer communication.

The proposed solution leverages a locally hosted Large Language Model (LLM) to ensure sensitive production data remains within the organization's infrastructure, making it suitable for regulated industries such as Banking and Insurance.

