8. Security

Security Principles

Local AI Deployment

All AI processing occurs within the enterprise network.

No Cloud AI

No production information is transmitted to external AI services.

Data Privacy

Sensitive operational and customer data remains on company-managed infrastructure.

Human Approval

Every AI-generated RCA and client communication requires manual approval before release.

Audit Logging

Comprehensive logs capture:

- Incident processing
- AI outputs
- User approvals
- Communication history

Role-Based Access Control

Access is restricted based on organizational roles:

- Production Support Engineers
- Team Leads
- Managers
- Administrators

